698
01:21:23,764 --> 01:21:29,340
I think we'll really love New York.

699
01:21:37,712 --> 01:21:39,692
When do we leave?

700
01:22:00,269 --> 01:22:02,145
I'm sorry.

701
01:22:09,044 --> 01:22:10,717
Tomorrow night.

