707
01:24:05,566 --> 01:24:08,479
So we decide to start again.

708
01:24:09,603 --> 01:24:11,981
Wipe the slate clean.

709
01:24:13,073 --> 01:24:14,950
Start afresh.

710
01:24:18,278 --> 01:24:20,349
